{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.delab\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">delab</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">optionsPerPos</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/SubExpr.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.OptionsPerPos\">Delaborator.OptionsPerPos</a> := <a href=\"./Init/Core.html#EmptyCollection.emptyCollection\">∅</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Meta/Defs.html#Lean.Syntax.Term\">Term</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"\"Delaborate\" the given term into surface-level syntax using the default and given subterm-specific options. ","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.delab","kind":"def","line":536,"name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.delab","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L536-L539"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.delabCore\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">delabCore</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">optionsPerPos</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/SubExpr.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.OptionsPerPos\">Delaborator.OptionsPerPos</a> := <a href=\"./Init/Core.html#EmptyCollection.emptyCollection\">∅</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">delab</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.DelabM\">Delaborator.DelabM</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> (<span class=\"fn\">α</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/SubExpr.html#Lean.SubExpr.PosMap\">SubExpr.PosMap</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree/Types.html#Lean.Elab.Info\">Elab.Info</a></span>)</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.delabCore","kind":"def","line":503,"name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.delabCore","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L503-L534"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.delabLevel\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">delabLevel</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">l</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Level.html#Lean.Level\">Level</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">prec</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Meta/Defs.html#Lean.Syntax.Level\">Syntax.Level</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.delabLevel","kind":"def","line":498,"name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.delabLevel","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L498-L501"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">opaque</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.appUnexpanderAttribute\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">appUnexpanderAttribute</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/KeyedDeclsAttribute.html#Lean.KeyedDeclsAttribute\">KeyedDeclsAttribute</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Unexpander\">Unexpander</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Registers an unexpander for applications of a given constant.\n\n`@[app_unexpander c]` registers a `Lean.PrettyPrinter.Unexpander` for applications of the constant\n`c`. The unexpander is passed the result of pre-pretty printing the application *without*\nimplicitly passed arguments. If `pp.explicit` is set to true or `pp.notation` is set to false,\nit will not be called at all.\n\nUnexpanders work as an alternative for delaborators (`@[app_delab]`) that can be used without\nspecial imports. This however also makes them much less capable since they can only transform\nsyntax and don't have access to the expression tree.\n","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.appUnexpanderAttribute","kind":"opaque","line":469,"name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.appUnexpanderAttribute","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L469-L491"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.delabLevel\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">delabLevel</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">l</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Level.html#Lean.Level\">Level</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">prec</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.DelabM\">DelabM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Meta/Defs.html#Lean.Syntax.Level\">Syntax.Level</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.delabLevel","kind":"def","line":465,"name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.delabLevel","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L465-L467"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">partial def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.delab\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">delab</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.Delab\">Delab</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.delab","kind":"opaque","line":437,"name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.delab","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L437-L463"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">partial def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.delabFor\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">delabFor</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a> → <a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.Delab\">Delab</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.delabFor","kind":"opaque","line":430,"name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.delabFor","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L430-L435"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.omission\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">omission</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">reason</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.OmissionReason\">OmissionReason</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.Delab\">Delab</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Delaborates the current expression as `⋯` and attaches `Elab.OmissionInfo`, which influences how the\nsubterm omitted by `⋯` is delaborated when hovered over.\n","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.omission","kind":"def","line":420,"name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.omission","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L420-L428"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.shouldOmitProof\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">shouldOmitProof</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.DelabM\">DelabM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Returns `true` if the given expression is a proof and should be omitted.\nThis function only returns `true` if `pp.proofs` is set to `false`.\n\n\"Shallow\" proofs are not omitted.\nThe `pp.proofs.threshold` option controls the depth threshold for what constitutes a shallow proof.\nSee `Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.isShallowExpression`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.shouldOmitProof","kind":"def","line":399,"name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.shouldOmitProof","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L399-L418"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.shouldOmitExpr\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">shouldOmitExpr</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.DelabM\">DelabM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Returns `true` if, at the current depth, we should omit the term and use `⋯` rather than\ndelaborating it. This function can only return `true` if `pp.deepTerms` is set to `false`.\nIt also contains a heuristic to allow \"shallow terms\" to be delaborated, even if they appear deep in\nan expression, which prevents terms such as atomic expressions or `OfNat.ofNat` literals from being\ndelaborated as `⋯`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.shouldOmitExpr","kind":"def","line":375,"name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.shouldOmitExpr","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L375-L397"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.isShallowExpression\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">isShallowExpression</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">threshold</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Returns true if `e` is a \"shallow\" expression.\nLocal variables, constants, and other atomic expressions are always shallow.\nIn general, an expression is considered to be shallow if its depth is at most `threshold`.\n\nSince the implementation uses `Lean.Expr.approxDepth`, the `threshold` is clamped to `[0, 254]`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.isShallowExpression","kind":"def","line":362,"name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.isShallowExpression","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L362-L373"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.withIncDepth\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">withIncDepth</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">act</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.DelabM\">DelabM</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.DelabM\">DelabM</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Runs the delaborator `act` with increased depth.\nThe depth is used when `pp.deepTerms` is `false` to determine what is a deep term.\nSee also `Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.Context.depth`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.withIncDepth","kind":"def","line":354,"name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.withIncDepth","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L354-L360"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.addOmissionInfo\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">addOmissionInfo</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">pos</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/SubExpr.html#Lean.SubExpr.Pos\">SubExpr.Pos</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">stx</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Syntax\">Syntax</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">reason</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.OmissionReason\">OmissionReason</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/D