Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">OmissionReason</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.OmissionReason","kind":"inductive","line":339,"name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.OmissionReason","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L339-L343"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.withBindingBodyUnusedName\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">withBindingBodyUnusedName</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">d</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Syntax\">Syntax</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.DelabM\">DelabM</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">preserveName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool.false\">false</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">avoid</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Data/NameMap/Basic.html#Lean.NameSet\">NameSet</a> := <a href=\"./Init/Core.html#EmptyCollection.emptyCollection\">∅</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.DelabM\">DelabM</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Enters the body of the current expression, which must be a lambda or forall.\nThe binding variable is passed to `d` as `Syntax`, and it is an identifier that has been annotated with the fvar expression\nfor the variable.\n\nIf `pp.safeShadowing` is true, then the name is allowed to shadow a name in the local context\nif the name does not appear in the body or in the `avoid` set.\n(The `avoid` set is assumed to be a subset of the names used by the local context.)\n\nIf `preserveName` is `false` (the default), gives the binder an unused name.\nOtherwise, it tries to preserve the textual form of the name, preserving whether it is hygienic.\n","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.withBindingBodyUnusedName","kind":"def","line":323,"name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.withBindingBodyUnusedName","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L323-L337"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.mkAnnotatedIdent\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">mkAnnotatedIdent</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.DelabM\">DelabM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Meta/Defs.html#Lean.Syntax.Ident\">Ident</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Creates an identifier that is annotated with the term `e`, using a fresh position using the `HoleIterator`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.mkAnnotatedIdent","kind":"def","line":314,"name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.mkAnnotatedIdent","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L314-L321"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.getUnusedName\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">getUnusedName</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">suggestion</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">body</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">preserveName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool.false\">false</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">avoid</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Data/NameMap/Basic.html#Lean.NameSet\">NameSet</a> := <a href=\"./Init/Core.html#EmptyCollection.emptyCollection\">∅</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.DelabM\">DelabM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Gets an name based on `suggestion` that is unused in the local context.\nErases macro scopes.\nIf `pp.safeShadowing` is true, then the name is allowed to shadow a name in the local context\nif the name does not appear in `body` or in the `avoid` set.\n(The `avoid` set is assumed to be a subset of the names used by the local context.)\n\nIf `preserveName` is false, then returns the name, possibly with fresh macro scopes added.\nIf `suggestion` has macro scopes then the result does as well.\n","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.getUnusedName","kind":"def","line":279,"name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.getUnusedName","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L279-L312"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.withAnnotateTermInfoUnlessAnnotated\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">withAnnotateTermInfoUnlessAnnotated</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">d</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.Delab\">Delab</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.Delab\">Delab</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Modifies the delaborator so that it ensures resulting term is annotated using `annotateTermInfoUnlessAnnotated`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.withAnnotateTermInfoUnlessAnnotated","kind":"def","line":272,"name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.withAnnotateTermInfoUnlessAnnotated","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L272-L277"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.withAnnotateTermInfo\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">withAnnotateTermInfo</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">d</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.Delab\">Delab</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.Delab\">Delab</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Modifies the delaborator so that it annotates the resulting term using `annotateTermInfo`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.withAnnotateTermInfo","kind":"def","line":265,"name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.withAnnotateTermInfo","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L265-L270"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.annotateTermInfoUnlessAnnotated\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">annotateTermInfoUnlessAnnotated</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">stx</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Meta/Defs.html#Lean.Syntax.Term\">Term</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.Delab\">Delab</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Annotates the term with the current expression position and registers `TermInfo`\nto associate the term to the current expression, unless the syntax has a synthetic position\nand associated `Info` already.\n","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.annotateTermInfoUnlessAnnotated","kind":"def","line":254,"name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.annotateTermInfoUnlessAnnotated","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L254-L263"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.annotateTermInfo\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">annotateTermInfo</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">stx</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Meta/Defs.html#Lean.Syntax.Term\">Term</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.Delab\">Delab</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Annotates the term with the current expression position and registers `TermInfo`\nto associate the term to the current expression.\n","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.annotateTermInfo","kind":"def","line":245,"name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.annotateTermInfo","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.lean#L245-L252"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Delaborator/Basic.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Delaborator.addDelabTermInfo\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">Delaborator</span>.<span class=\"name\">addDelabTermInfo</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">pos</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/SubExpr.html#Lean.SubExpr.Pos\">SubExpr.Pos</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">stx</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Syntax\">Syntax</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">isBinder</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool.false\">false</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">location?</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Data/DeclarationRange.html#Lean.DeclarationLocation\">DeclarationLocation</a></span> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option.none\">none</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">docString?</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a></span> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option.none\">none</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">mkDocString?</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Lean/Data/PPContext.html#Lean.PPContext\">PPContext</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/System/IO.htm